{"title":"桥（快板）","authors":["张崇纲"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":11,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"桥（快板）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山东省崂山县中韩公社社员　张崇纲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从我记事就知道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村西村上有座桥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爷爷踏它下关东，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爹爹被逼桥上逃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奶奶桥头跳河死，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我娘过桥把饭要。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"独木桥啊血泪桥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚踩泪泡已烂掉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮火漫天响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修起木板桥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过桥上前线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战马桥上跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桥上桥下飘红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我帮军队推大炮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打起鼓啊吹起号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"木板桥是解放桥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土改那年再修桥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石墩石座建得牢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫农踏它去下地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甩开牛鞭唱新调；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷人孩子进学堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红脸映得河水笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桥上走啊桥上过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头桥是翻身桥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社成立了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年更比一年好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深挖墩基粗打桩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢筋铁骨修大桥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"排排车队桥上飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我开“铁牛”哞哞叫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平平坦坦，轰轰隆隆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员走的是幸福桥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血泪桥，解放桥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻身桥，幸福桥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长辈踏着它打天下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们走得稳啊保得牢！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}